So why one-on-ones?

00:02:18.559 --> 00:02:20.960
Why do I want to talk about one-on-ones so much?

00:02:20.960 --> 00:02:26.800
Well, one-on-ones, in my experience, create trust, like you're talking to that other person,

00:02:26.800 --> 00:02:30.880
it's individual, you're talking about what matters, it's in a very specific context,

00:02:30.880 --> 00:02:35.880
that builds up trust over time, and that's the connective tissue that make really great

