executing at a high level, and I'll tell you, being part of a team that's executing

00:02:43.679 --> 00:02:48.919
at a high level is like the best kind of way to work and a lot, a lot of fun.

00:02:48.919 --> 00:02:51.639
So why one-on-ones though specifically?

