We got our feedback one we already talked about.

00:08:27.079 --> 00:08:28.600
We got our career conversations.

00:08:28.600 --> 00:08:32.239
I'm just going to call out one that I really personally have gotten a lot of value on,

00:08:32.239 --> 00:08:36.799
which is the in the middle for the check-in, any sneaky issues worrying you.

00:08:36.799 --> 00:08:38.599
So what do I mean by a sneaky issue?

00:08:38.599 --> 00:08:41.359
That's something that's small, maybe in the back of someone's mind.

00:08:41.359 --> 00:08:43.440
It's kind of picking at them and picking at them.

00:08:43.440 --> 00:08:44.440
It's not a big deal.

00:08:44.440 --> 00:08:48.919
You don't need to bring it up yet, but it's simmering, it's simmering, and then it boils

00:08:48.919 --> 00:08:49.919
over.

00:08:49.919 --> 00:08:51.919
And once it boils over, it's actually a big problem.

00:08:51.919 --> 00:08:57.440
If you can ask questions that get you to those earlier simmering levels, it's much easier

00:08:57.440 --> 00:08:59.320
to address challenges.

00:08:59.320 --> 00:09:03.799
So that's just one of my personal favorites from this big list here.

