But if you build in the habits around them and give them a try and put the multiples

00:09:15.239 --> 00:09:18.280
together, you're going to get more out of one-on-ones, you're going to move your team

00:09:18.280 --> 00:09:19.280
forward.

00:09:19.280 --> 00:09:22.919
So the first tactic, topic scorecard, all you're going to do is take a list like that

